Feature: Get gatling report

    As Xray Connector,
    I want to create a single report from gatling test execution reports
    So that it may be uploaded into Xray

    # Rules:
    #
    # 1) gatling reports should be looked for in the feature files reports directory
    # 2) The merged report should be stored in the merged report directory
    # 3) The merged report should be named merged-output.json
    # 4) The merged report may be generated several times and overwritten
    # 5) The merged report directory should be created if necessary
    # 6) The merged report directory may be a subdirectory of the feature files reports directory
    # 7) The feature files reports directory may be a subdirectory of the merged report directory

    Scenario: Generate gatling merged report

        Given The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features'
        And   The merged report directory is 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged'
        And   The gatling reports directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/gatling'
        And   The gatling simulation main class is 'GenericTest'

        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features' has been created
        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged' has been created
        And   Xray Connector has retrieved feature files from Xray as a zipfile

        When  Xray Connector writes down feature files present in zipfile
        And   Xray Connector creates merged report from gatling reports

        Then  File 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features/ACTIVE/1.feature' should exist
        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged' should exist
        And   File 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged/merged-output.json' should exist

    Scenario: Generate gatling merged report for invalid feature files directory

        Given The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/unknown'
        And   The merged report directory is 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged'
        And   The gatling reports directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/gatling'
        And   The gatling simulation main class is 'GenericTest'

        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features' has been created
        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged' has been created
        And   Xray Connector has retrieved feature files from Xray as a zipfile

        When  Xray Connector creates merged report from gatling reports

        Then  Directory 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged' should exist
        And   File 'tmp/cucumber/reports/merged/merged-output.json' should exist

